{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"0602a828bf619ea2c914a5a127be7576","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I now have a good understanding of the current state. The project has:\n\n1. **Database Schema**: Complete with all tables (users, profiles, products, images, transactions, etc.)\n2. **Auth Setup**: Better Auth configured\n3. **UI Components**: Basic shadcn/ui components (button, input, card, label)\n4. **Tailwind CSS**: Already set up with v4\n\nWhat's still needed (according to the fix_plan.md):\n- Impeccable design规范安装\n- OpenSpec初始化\n- 数据库迁移到PostgreSQL (阿里云ECS)\n- 路由保护中间件\n- 阿里云OSS集成\n- 落地页开发\n- 客户端功能\n- 管理端功能\n- AI对接\n\nBased on the project plan, the current priorities are Phase 1 (基础框架搭建).\n\nLet me understand what the user wants me to do. They seem to be showing me the project plan and current status. Let me ask what they want to work on first, or I could help them start with the Phase 1 tasks.\n\nActually, looking at the project again - it seems they've already done a lot of groundwork. Let me check what tasks I should help with and ask the user what they want to do.\n\nThe current status shows:\n- Basic Next.js setup: ✅ Done\n- Dependencies installed: ✅ Done\n- Database schema: ✅ Done  \n- Auth: ✅ Done\n- Basic UI components: ✅ Done\n- Tailwind: ✅ Done\n\nWhat needs to be done:\n- Install Impeccable\n- Set up OpenSpec\n- Switch from SQLite to PostgreSQL\n- Create middleware for auth\n- Integrate OSS\n- Build landing page\n- Client features\n- Admin features\n\nLet me ask the user what they want to work on.","signature":"46e427e253427c7ab1a190f2b1b88dd25bd7de42424292cd853396e5396eff2e"}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.5","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":387,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1663,"cache_read_input_tokens":33237},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2173432b-ac44-46b4-9b3f-0bb626a203f4","uuid":"dbf251e3